_sText:
Took me about a day to make a beta for this map. Based off a very old 1.6 map "sb_dunes". Should be a lot of fun to play, incredibly optimized i get a straight 299 FPS (capped at 299) as you can see from the screenies.
Features
  • Custom lighting
  • Light dust clouds
  • Fully built cubemaps
  • Custom Navigation Mesh
  • Surrounding areas acting like a 3d skybox.
